cause.description:
When all else failed: 

Tony Iommi laid a sonic bridge through our estranged neural circuitry to the dark castle in our hearts;
Ronnnie James Dio lived in there even although sometimes we didn't notice (not just because he is so short but because sometimes King Diamond took his place); 
Dave Lombardo's double bass work scared both those dudes out of there;
Then our hearts were empty again and we continued searching until we found... Tool.  We began to rebuild.

(To be continued)



1. Heavy Metal music Rocks!!!

2. Longhair can be worn on the inside!!

3. Flash Metal to your family, friends, and colleagues!!
